            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Hd1e108">Rubrica 37</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De confessione et indulgentia peccatorum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>¶ De confessione et indul
      <lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>gentia peccatorum. Rubrica 37
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/> <ref>PSalmista. pslamus 31.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e125">Be
        <lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>ati quorum re
        <lb ed="#V" n="86" break="no"/>misse sunt iniquitates: et quorum te
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>cta sunt peccata.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e135"> /
      <ref>117 psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e137">Confi
        <lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>temini domino quoniam bonus: quoniam in saeculum misericordia eius.
      </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e144">
               <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>
               ¶ <ref>Salomon in prouer. c. 28.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e148">Qui abscondit scele
        <lb ed="#V" n="90" break="no"/>ra sua non dirigetur. Qui autem confessus fuerit et 
        <!--53.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="13-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>reliquerit ea misericordiam consequetur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e162"> /
      <ref>Idem in eccl. c. 10.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e164">Curatio cessare facit peccata maxima.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e170">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
               ¶ <ref>Iesus fi. sirach in ec. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e174">Non confundar confiteri
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>peccata tua.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e180"> /
      <ref>c. 17.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e182">Uiuus et sanus confiteberis
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>et laudabis deum et glorificaberis in miserationibus illius</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e188">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>
               ¶ <ref>Mattheus in euan. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e192">Si dimiseritis homini
        <lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>bus peccata eorum: dimittet et vobis pater vester
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>celestis delicta vestra. Si autem non dimiseritis
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>hominibus nec pater vester dimittet peccata vestra. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e202">
               <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>
               ¶ <ref>Marcus in euan. c. 11.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e206">Cum stabitis ad oran
        <lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>dum dimittite siquid habetis aduersus aliquem: vt
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>pater vs qui in caelis est dimittat vobis peccata vestra.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e215">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
               ¶ <ref>Lucas in euang. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e219">Dimittite et dimittetur
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>vobis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e225"> /
      <ref>c. 17.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e227">Si peccauerit fratur tuus in te
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>increpa illum: et si paenitentiam egerit dimitte illi: et
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>si septies in die peccauerit in te: et septies in die
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>conuersus fuerit ad te dicens penitet me: di
        <lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>mitte illi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e239">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>
               ¶ <ref>Ioannes in epistola. i. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e243">Si confiteamur peccatam
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>nostra fidelis et iustus est dominus vt remittat nobis
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>peccata nostra: et emundet nos ab omni iniquitate.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e251">
               <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>
               ¶ <ref>Iacobus apostolus epistola vnica. c. 5. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e255">Confi
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>teamini alterutrum peccata vestra.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e261">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>
               ¶ <ref>Paulus apostolus epsitola ad Ro. c. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e265">Corde cre
        <lb ed="#V" n="25" break="no"/>ditur ad iustitiam: ore autem confessio fit ad salutem.
      </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e271">
               <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>
               ¶ <ref>Isidorus in sinonima soliloquiorum li. i. c. 12</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e275">Confessio sanat: confessio iustificat animum: confes
        <lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>sio peccatis veniam donat. Nulla tam grauis est cul
        <lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>pa quae non habeat veniam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e286"> /
      <ref>c. 16. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e288">Frequenter
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>peccatis et lugens veniam vix meretur.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
